<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَي نَزَع عَنهُ اللَّحْمَ،<span class="c5"> وأَنشدَ الجَوْهَرِيُّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وعَامُنا أَعْجَبَنَا مُقَدَّمَهْ ... )</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(يُدعَى أَبَا السَّمْحِ وقِرْضَابٌ سُمُهْ ... )</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(مُبْتَرِكًا لِكُلّ عَظْمٍ يَلْحُمُهْ ... )</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> لَحَمَ القَومَ، <span class="c2">(كَمَنَعَ)</span> يَلْحَمُهُمْ لَحْمًا: <span class="c2">(أَطْعَمَ اللَّحْم،<span class="c5"> فَهُو:</span> لَاحِمٌ)</span> ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ الجوهَرِيُّ:</span> وَلَا تَقُل أَلْحَمْتُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> والأصْمَعِيّ يَقُولُه،<span class="c5"> قَالَ شَمِرٌ:</span> والقِيَاسُ: لَحَمْتُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> مِنَ المَجازِ: لَحِم، <span class="c2">(كَعَلِمَ)</span> ، لَحْمًا إِذا <span class="c2">(نَشِبَ فِي المَكَانِ)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> قَالَ أَبُو سَعِيد: يُقالُ: <span class="c2">(هَذَا)</span> الكَلَامُ <span class="c2">(لَحِيمُ هَذَا)</span> الكَلَام وطَرِيدُه،<span class="c5"> كَأَمِيرٍ أَيْ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَفْقُه وشَكْلُه)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(وأَبُو اللَّحَّامِ التَّغْلَبِيُّ، كَشَدَّادٍ)</span> ،<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي بَعْضِ النُّسَخ الثَّعْلَبِيّ:</span> <span class="c2">(شَاعِرٌ)</span> فارِسٌ فِي الجَاهِلِيَّة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> مِنَ المَجازِ: <span class="c2">(اسْتَلْحَمَ الطَّرِيقَ)</span> إذَا <span class="c2">(تَبِعَه)</span> أَو رَكِبَه ولَزِمَه، كَمَا فِي الأَسَاس، <span class="c2">(أَو تَبِعَ أَوْسَعَةُ)</span> ولَزِمه،<span class="c5"> قَالَ رُؤْبَةُ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(ومَنْ أَرْيَناهُ الطَّرِيقَ استَلْحَمَا ... )</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ امرؤُ القَيْسِ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(استَلْحَمَ الوَحْشَ على أَكْسَائِها ... أهوَجُ مِحَضِيرٌ إِذا النَّقْعُ دَخَنْ)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي حَدِيثِ أُسَامَة:</span> <span class="c1">" فاستَلْحَمَنَا رَجلٌ من العَدُوِّ "</span> أَي: تَبِعَنَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> استَلْحَمَ <span class="c2">(الطَّرِيقُ: اتَّسَعَ)</span> .<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> من المَجازِ: <span class="c2">(استُلْحِمَ)</span> الرَّجلُ، <span class="c2">(مَجْهُولاً)</span> إِذَا <span class="c2">(رُوهِقَ فِي القِتَالِ)</span> ،<span class="c5"> وَفِي الصِّحَاحِ:</span> احْتَوَشَهُ العَدُوُّ فِي القِتَالِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>